      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That doesn't make sense. My team checked the dock and the receiving logs multiple times yesterday and there was absolutely nothing. Are you sure you're looking at the right tracking number? If this is a mistake on your end, we're going to have to charge Global Ship for the delay and the downtime for our staff.",
